{"tid":328686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日澳門　明日香港　立法會　意見限六類　要提前通知　禁道具","createTime":"2017-07-19T18:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T17:33:23.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7974839381dc4468e6dd379c16b69956b4703173","tid":328686,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mastvnet.com/video/news/2017-7-17/video_content_176513.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmastvnet.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2F2017-7-17%2Fvideo_content_176513.shtml&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=387fd396\" target=\"_blank\">http://mastvnet.com/video/news/2017-7-17/video_content_176513.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：澳亞衛視<br />\n<br />\n　　以往在立法會中，經常都有議員在座位上放著抗議標語，無論是立法會全體大會，甚至是施政答問大會，這種表達訴求的方式存在多年，最早期由民主派議員發起，到現在愈來愈多議員加入，不過這道立法會內獨有的風景線，很可能從下屆立法會開始，從此就要消失。因為立法會章程及任期委員會17日宣佈，為了立法會的莊嚴和威信，全數禁用這些道具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chengpou.com.mo/cp-page/dailynews/?d=94508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chengpou.com.mo%2Fcp-page%2Fdailynews%2F%3Fd%3D94508&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=979b186e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chengpou.com.mo/cp-page/dailynews/?d=94508</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：正報<br />\n<br />\n心意表達也設限 (18/07/2017)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】章程及任期委員會就議會運作提出多項改善、優化建議，除禁用道具外，還建議修改經常為建制議員詬病的「表達心意」的適用範圍明確限於祝賀、慰唁等六大範疇，並要提前通知，不再像現行般不設限。<br />\n<br />\n現行《議事規則》規定：「任何議員均可提議表達心意，尤其是表達祝賀、慰唁、抗議、致意、讚揚或譴責等。」可謂在這方面的提案範圍不設限，也沒有時間方面的限制，只須會前提出即可。<br />\n<br />\n據委會主席黃顯輝介紹，今次建議取消當中的「尤其」、「等」的字眼，訂明表達心意限定於表祝賀、慰唁、抗議、致意、讚揚和譴責六大類。過去曾有議員就撤回離補法、啟動政改等提表達心意，一度被人批評不符致意的目的。<br />\n<br />\n致意要提前廿四小時通知<br />\n<br />\n同時建議就表達心意的提案加設時間限制，必須要會議召開前至少廿四小時前通知立法會。黃顯輝解釋，這樣安排「純粹」是為讓提案有時間去翻譯、知會每位議員，「係建議程序上做好呢個工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/CPJv3a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCPJv3a&h=d7099f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://aamacau.com/2017/07/17/立法會又要自我閹割？-大會期間禁用道具-干預表/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%88%E8%A6%81%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E9%96%B9%E5%89%B2%EF%BC%9F-%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E9%81%93%E5%85%B7-%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E8%A1%A8%2F&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=b1055a31\" target=\"_blank\">http://aamacau.com/2017/07/17/立法會又要自我閹割？-大會期間禁用道具-干預表/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/posts/1379933028742461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacauconcealers%2Fposts%2F1379933028742461%2F&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=e44b977b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/posts/1379933028742461/</a><br />\n<br />\n【愛瞞報道】有損議會莊嚴威信嗎? 澳門立會建議修例 禁止議員在大會上展示道具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/posts/501846503491893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau%2Fposts%2F501846503491893&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=094467e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau/posts/501846503491893</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：澳門方丈聯盟<br />\n<br />\n香港non stop DQ議員當然打橫來<br />\n聽教聽話的澳門更不遑多讓<br />\n<br />\n現在個立法會<br />\n除咗表決通過惡法之外<br />\n就來連意見都唔比表達了...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5kwh9pp1AmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5kwh9pp1AmU&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=1f780b65\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5kwh9pp1AmU</a><br />\n方丈講場 特別消息 2017-07-19 澳門議事規則收緊"},{"pid":"3bc2cf5992315b57d29e14e6b2f9c7148bf30342","tid":328686,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d49fde